      "citation": "Ps 18:2-3, 3-4, 47, 51, R. v.2\nI love you, Lord, my strength.",
      "summary": "",
      "antiphon": "Ps 18:2-3, 3-4, 47, 51, R. v.2\nI love you, Lord, my strength."
    },
    {
